my fellow citizen :
hello , everyone ! we all know the " september 18 th " incident , but now japan again have a premeditate plan for another " september 18 th " on the sea , another " lugou bridge on the sea ".
japan surprisingly defy the strong condemnation of the whole world , openly invade our country 's sacred territory , " the diaoyu island ".
as we all know , the " diaoyu island " have always belong to china ; due to historical reason , what originally belong us have become controversial .
my fellow citizen , ours be ours , what need be there to negotiate ! japan thus go even further - want to create a fact of occupation . can we allow this ? no - absolutely not !
my fellow citizen , japan 's militarism have bring the people of asia grave disaster .
especially china suffer the ravage of japan for as long as several decade .
in the northeast , japanese unit 731 cruelly conduct human body experiment on live people of china , korea and other country , the method of which be extremely brutal ; the nanjing massacre add a layer of blood to the ancient capital which will never fade away ; the big bloody battle at hengyang and changsha lay bare the bone of the dead over a thousand kilometers and kill off everything ...
my fellow citizen , of the heinous crime commit by japan in china , there be too many instance to cite , difficult to record without exhaust all bamboo strip .
it 's just as if those ten million decease soul who lost their life be wander over the pacific ocean , find it difficult to rest in peace .
all the people who experience that era must still remember it vividly ; even our younger generation also will cry with tear stream down our cheek , and our blood boil with indignation , whenever we turn to this page of history and read !
now japan actually want to reverse the verdict on the history of its aggression - fellow citizen , fellow chinese in asia , wake up !
although it be painful to look back at these hundred year of shame , we must go face it ; although historical issue have not be resolve , let us create and choose history !
since there be responsibility , we be not afraid . the territory be small , but it be relate to the matter of dignity ; no matter how the wind and cloud change , the interest of the country and national unity be the guarantee of honor ; even though scar with wound , we can not let our native land be separate !
my fellow citizen , for the chinese nation , the advent of the twenty @-@ first century mean a time when we be beset with difficulty inside while be press from outside , and we will face many challenge .
the taiwan issue , the tibet issue , the south china sea issue , the surround environment , as well as the foreign force which be aggressive to china - which way should we go ?
what to do , fellow citizen ? please take a look at the map of the world , that crescent @-@ shape encirclement be suppress our breathe , strangle our development , and covet our national territory .
we do not want to make enemy , but be never afraid of enemy ; we do not want war , but be never afraid of war .
we must urgently arrange arm , strengthen all military force on land , on sea , and in the air .
over thousand of year , the chinese nation have flourish several time , but before it have never have ambition to expand its territory outward .
not impose on others what we do n't want ourselves , what we follow be a foreign security strategic philosophy which apply benevolence and virtue .
the tolerance and liberalness of a country be like those of an individual - we avoid hurt others , but must insist on not be hurt ourselves .
tolerance be certainly not fear , and sincerity do not have to be cowardice .
china exempt japan from war reparation for world war ii be in service of peace , benevolent peace .
my fellow citizen , the people 's hero monument be a condense history of the chinese nation strive for continuous self @-@ improvement
the solemn and magnificent posture represent a sacred expectation for peace .
the thought @-@ string of my memory have be agitate from time to time - many heroic , stir , and tragic scene of shine spear and armored horse spring up in my mind .
my thought go through those yellow page of history , as if i see emperor kangxi , the famous ruler of a generation , contemplate alone about how to achieve unification of the territory in his audience hall , hundred of year ago ; also as if i see abraham lincoln , former u.s. president , wander alone in the dark of a great hall , think about the integrity of the union .
" although it be peaceful throughout the world , it be certainly dangerous to forget war ! " my fellow citizen , we want development and peace , but we must never exercise forbearance blindly . the " boxer protocol " of national betrayal and humiliation have aggravate china 's poverty and backwardness in modern time - fall behind will lead to be bully .
without strength , where do peace come from !
we must focus on national defense education , build up a great wall in the heart of 1.3 billion people , and must establish the full range of a national defense system have the ability to both attack and defend ;
the best defense be to attack - we should strengthen force which can engage in ultra @-@ long @-@ range attack , improve combat capability throughout all of aerospace , of great depth , and over great distance . on the premise of avoid influence on national economic development , increase investment and construction of the defense industry , accelerate modernization and internationalization of military equipment , and establish a high @-@ quality , high @-@ tech elite division .
the battle horn be about to sound , the people be already fully equip and ready to go .
without the people 's support we will accomplish nothing ; with the support of the people , we will be all @-@ powerful .
my fellow citizen , it be time for us to say " no " to others . therefore , we must achieve :
1. establish guarantee fund , improve work environment and mechanism , recruit back to china the hundred of thousand of it professional who have emigrate to and linger in the unite state and around the world .
2. create a few nuclear @-@ power aircraft carrier battle group .
3. manufacture 5000 advance combat aircraft of various kind .
4. accelerate the research and deployment of high @-@ speed intercontinental ballistic missile which can break missile defense system and whose range be more than 10,000 nautical mile .
5. resume nuclear experiment , and establish military force in space .
6. retain 1000 nuclear bomb equivalent to ten million ton of tnt , and when necessary , install nuclear warhead on all short @- and middle @-@ range missile .
7. retain 30 strategic nuclear submarine with the ability to inflict three devastate nuclear strike against enemy .
8. abandon the commitment to not use nuclear weapon first .
9. retain the right of pre @-@ emptive strike when national security be threaten .
my fellow citizen , only if we have self @-@ confidence and self @-@ improvement , can we strive to be strong . qin shi huang unify china . zheng chenggong recover taiwan . in our responsibility we must carry on the farsightedness , insight , and strong will of our predecessor .
now , that piece of land tremble far away from the embrace of the motherland be shake , moan , and call . fellow citizen , let us carry forward the unfulfilled wish of previous general , move forward courageously !
when read over history , the heaviness and anger in my heart simmer into concern for the nation . although i be born to cloth gown and am one of the common people , for the prosperity of the motherland , for the motherland be splendid once again , i be willing to voluntarily serve our country , and i will have no regret even if i die ! my sincere patriotic heart be adequate to show to heaven !
