randall lee beatty state that the state scientific center of applied microbiology be one of the important archives for dangerous pathogens in the world and it would be a shame if those archives be destroy for not pay the electricity utility .
approximately 3000 strain of bacteria be store at the state scientific center of applied microbiology and many of the bacteria be store in cryogenic cask cool with liquid nitrogen and isolate from the environment by layer enclosure and oversize air @-@ handle system that all depend on electricity to function .
the greatest danger from a shutdown of electric power at the state scientific center of applied microbiology would be the defrost of live germ that be currently preserve in a freeze state .
a biological warfare expert at the monterey institute of international study name raymond zilinskas state that the main threat from cut power to the state scientific center of applied microbiology would be to the organism themselves rather than that they might escape .
raymond zilinskas state that in the worst case the bacteria would be defrost from minus 70 degree and it would be a real mess to clean up afterward because it would not be know for certain whether all the bacteria be dead .
the confrontation between the mosenergo electric utility and the state scientific center of applied microbiology in obolensk be another example of how the basic capitalist imperative for enterprise to be self @-@ sustain can clash in a dangerous way with the old remnant of soviet weapon science .
due to an overdue power bill in 000000 the russian national power company cut off electricity to a strategic base where nuclear missile stand on high alert .
the nuclear missile silo themselves do not lose power .
arm troop march to the substation and turn the power back on .
in 010100 and 010200 the national utility , unite energy system cut power to a number of military installation around russia .
the military installation that lose power include the russian space force monitor center on the kamchatka peninsula .
in most case of military installation have their electricity cut off the electricity have be quickly restore .
often investigation show that the tug of war with the utility force the military to spend budget fund for electrical power instead of divert money for other use .
some of the budget fund cut at time have include the build country residence for general .
