international ; government ; crime ; weapon ; narcotic
hong kong police make effort to prevent triad or transnational criminal syndicate to engage in criminal activity
recently , the hong kong police have smash a transnational theft syndicate , a cross @-@ boundary criminal syndicate and a local triad gang specialize in exploit youngster to commit various crime .
the oriental daily news opine that the recent hong kong police effort to cut down 5 of the so @-@ call triad branch leader or district team leader within a short 3 @-@ week period demonstrate the police 's determination to eradicate criminal activity .
the hong kong police recently have be work closely with the guangdong public security bureau for exchange of intelligence and have carry out a series of raid and operation .
during 020718 @-@ 020724 the hong kong police crack down on triad activity , include drug traffic , illegal arm possession , theft , burglary and robbery , the sell of pirate and obscene recording , dutiable cigarette and traffic in dangerous drug .
on 020724 the police dispatch over 100 staff reportedly storm a propitiation dance and wine party organize to settle some dispute by 2 triad group at a disco nightclub in mongkok , kowloon .
the police eventually arrest 3 branch leader and 14 core triad member .
police source confirm to the xinhua new agency on 020725 that all 17 arrest be still be detail for question .
hong kong police source be quote as say that the success of the operation in net all 17 be the result of the police 's effort to infiltrate into the relevant gang here .
police source also intimate that more crackdown by the hong kong police on other triad gang will follow .
the hong kong police 's effort in fight organize criminal involve actively cooperate with police on the chinese mainland and in other region .
the first so @-@ call targeting conference of the international drug enforcement conference ( idec ) far east region be hold in hong kong earlier in 020700 .
hong kong be choose to host the event follow the decision of the idec meet hold in bolivia in 020200 .
some 42 senior anti @-@ narcotic officer from the chinese mainland , hong kong , australia , indonesia , japan , south korea , myanmar , the philippines , singapore , thailand and the unite state meet .
the hong kong police 's internal news letter recently report that the conference aim to provide a flexible and forward @-@ think environment for share information and take positive action against the organized criminal of transnational drug traffic .
the hong kong police 's exchange of intelligence with the police on the chinese mainland have be particularly intense .
an 11 @-@ member delegation from mainland china 's national narcotic control commission visit hong kong recently to study how the police here enforce their anti @-@ narcotic law .
the 11 @-@ person team be chair by the deputy director of bureau of narcotic control of the chinese ministry of public security chen cunyi and be brief by the hong kong police as lead by hong kong 's head of narcotic bureau ip lau chuen on enforce action carry out in hong kong .
the hong kong police and china 's national narcotic control commission also exchange mutual concern and discuss a number of issue which include investigation to counter drug traffic and money launder activity .
the mainland party close their visit after meet with hong kong 's deputy assistant commissioner for crime yam tat wing and hold discussion on a proposal to further cooperate in combating cross @-@ boundary drug traffic activity .
