international ; terrorism ; politics
chinese foreign minister tang jiaxuan report that the member country of the shanghai cooperation organization will proceed with the construction of the sco and begin anti @-@ terrorism discussion at a meet in moscow on 23 november 2002 .
chinese foreign minister tang jiaxuan state on 23 november 2002 that the member state of the shanghai cooperation organization ( sco ) have progress in the construction of the organization and the cooperation among member nation .
tang and 5 foreign minister from russia , kazakhstan , kyrgyzstan , tajikistan and uzbekistan will meet in moscow on 23 november 2002 for discussion of the sco 's construction and a series of international and regional issue .
tang state that mechanism construction be the current focus for sco and that preparation work for create a secretariat have enter a key stage under the joint effort of coordinators and expert from the 6 country .
tang also state the chinese government seek to complete the draft of relevant document before next year 's sco summit and to attempt to officially open the secretariat after the summit .
tang state the sco still face a very stern anti @-@ terrorism fight and cite the october 2002 hostage crisis in moscow .
tang state the fact that the terrorist attack in moscow be mastermind by national separatist and regional extremist demonstrate the necessity and correctness of effort in reduce the 3 @-@ force of terrorism , separatism and extremism .
tang state that all sco member should deepen and expand security cooperation by adopt deal on jointly fight against the 3 @-@ force and terrorist organization and by create a regional anti @-@ terrorist organization in kyrgyz capital bishkek as soon as possible .
tang state that the chinese government appreciate and support some central asian country ' proposal on enhance anti @-@ drug cooperation .
tang state that the chinese government sign multilateral anti @-@ drug cooperation pact .
tang state anti @-@ drug measure as one of the top task of regional anti @-@ terrorist organization .
tang state that economic cooperation be a key area for cooperation between the sco member , state --
to gain substantial benefit from economic and trade cooperation , all member state should strengthen political common sense over economic and trade cooperation and regard economic and trade cooperation as a strategic problem that could affect regional security and the sco 's development .
tang also referenced a volatile world situation and state that the common and press task of all sco member be to manage threat from untraditional security sphere include terrorism , drug traffic , weapon smuggle , transnational monetary crime .
tang state that peace and development still dominate the current age as the general situation of the world be stable and the economy be develop forward in wave .
tang state that the international community be watch the organization closely as more country and international organization be willing to conduct dialogue and cooperation with the sco .
tang state that the sco should further enhance the exchange and cooperation with other party through wide visibility and a more positive post , which may not only strengthen sco 's international influence but also reflect sco 's principle of no @-@ alignment , not @-@ against @-@ a @-@ third @-@ party and open @-@ up .
tang state that the sco will pass a temporary pact on sco 's foreign policy at the meet on 23 november 2002 .
tang state that the pact will officially start the sco 's exchange activity with other organization and promote the shanghai @-@ spirit of mutual trust and benefit , equality , cooperation , multicultural respect and the search for common development .
