accord to the record osama bin laden 's brother sheik mohammed khalid have be able to travel in and out of the country a number of time .
sheik mohammed khalid be allegedly fund terrorist network in the philippines .
the military and police have be place on high alert for the holy week start april 5 , 2004 .
6 abu sayyaf suspect be capture last week in separate raid in metro manila .
the suspect ' plot to launch terrorist attack allegedly as devastate as the madrid bombings in spain be foil .
president gloria macapagal @-@ arroyo say in a statement on april 7 , 2004 that the government be closely watch foreigner in the country who may have teach the local rebel and terrorist to make bomb or have launder money from the al @-@ qaeda terrorist group .
abs @-@ cbn news channel be a local television station in manila .
2004 @-@ 04 @-@ 29
china ( cn ) ; germany ( de )
international ; government ; technology ; politics ; economy
chinese premier discuss plan for broad cooperation with important trade partner germany ahead of european visit .
wen state that the main purpose of the germany visit be to advance trade , economic and technological exchange .
in an interview with dieter stolte on 29 april 2004 chinese premier wen jiabao state that the government of china and germany should establish solid cooperation , enhance consultation on major international issue and further strengthen trade and technological exchange .
wen be interview before his imminent visit to europe by the publisher of die welt .
wen be schedule to visit 5 european nation include germany start 2 may 2004 .
wen state that the chinese people be familiar with germany particularly due to the profound influence of karl marx on china 's revolution and economic construction .
wen state that many world @-@ renowned thinker , writer , philosopher and artist be german .
wen state that forerunner of german classic philosophy gottfried leibnitz call china 's confucian think an influence on the enlightenment movement in 18 th century germany .
wen state that the purpose of his visit to germany be to advance trade , economic and technological exchange .
the government of china and germany be expect to further increase cooperation in this regard .
wen speak of his brief visit to frankfurt during a tour of nordic nation in 1988 and state that the friendship between china and germany be sincere , active and fruitful .
wen pledge to establish a development goal for sino @-@ german relation state that mutual trust constitute the foundation of bilateral relation .
wen state that trade between china and germany have amounted to 41.8 billion u.s. dollar totaling one @-@ third of china @-@ europe trade volume .
wen state that both china @-@ german and china @-@ europe trade be expect to double by 2010 .
wen state that the government of china and germany plan close cooperation in high @-@ tech research and development and among medium and small @-@ size enterprise .
wen state that it be important to create channel for settle trade dispute between the 2 country and that china and germany should address each other 's concern .
china consider germany the most important trade partner of europe .
to support this statement wen cite that 600 of the 7000 chinese enterprise that invest internationally be in germany .
wen state that the government of china will support enterprise which invest in germany with loan , insurance , foreign exchange , finance and investment .
chinese investment in germany be much less than german investment in china since china have only recently start invest in this respect .
wen state that german investment project in china have exceed 3500 with total investment near 10 billion u.s. dollar .
some german firm such as volkswagen , siemens and daimler @-@ chrysler have a reputation for high quality and efficiency .
wen state that chinese enterprise can make progress and learn modern management by cooperate with german partner .
wen state that germany be china 's close european partner in technology transfer .
wen state that china consider sino @-@ eu relation a crucial part of china 's diplomatic strategy and that china and europe develop a comprehensive strategic partnership in 2003 .
wen state that he be optimistic that the eu would lift the arm embargo on china soon and would give china market economy status .
wen state that the arm embargo be an outdate result of the cold war .
wen state that china be deeply concern with the current situation in iraq and be sympathetic to the iraqi people .
wen state that china and europe have similar position on the issue of iraq 's reconstruction .
wen state that the unite nation should play a dominant role in the process of iraq 's reconstruction and that every country should participate .
wen state that china be willing to participate in iraq 's reconstruction process .
wen state that it be easy to win a war but much more difficult to win peace .
wen state that he be deeply worry about the increase tension between palestine and israel and that the chinese government hope the dispute between the 2 country can be resolve through political negotiation so that the country can peacefully share land .
with regard to the situation in palestine and israel wen state that relevant un resolution must be implement .
wen state that the chinese government support plan for peace in the middle east and remain firmly oppose to violent retaliation .
when ask to comment on how to temper china 's rapidly grow economy and how to realize balance growth wen state that the chinese economy be very healthy in general with fast growth , increase corporate profit , improve agricultural production , expand foreign trade volume and rapidly grow fiscal revenue and individual income .
in order to restrict the excessive fix asset construction that cause a rise in capital good price and strain the supply of coal , electricity , oil and transportation , the chinese government will increase its macro economic control and employ all necessary administrative method .
wen state that the chinese government will control the loan and land supply and will advance reform in the structural and systematic cause of current economic problem .
with regard to the issue of social balance wen state that china 's new leadership have begin to resolve problem of coordination between urban and rural development and between different region and have focused on balance economic growth with social progress , domestic construction with external work , and development with respect for nature .
when ask to comment on german federal chancellor gerhard schroeder 's promise to support sale of nuclear fuel from hanau to china wen state that cooperation between china and germany in this field be exclusively for peaceful utilization of nuclear energy with equality and mutual benefit .
2004 @-@ 09 @-@ 22
china ( cn ) ; kyrgyzstan ( kg )
international ; government ; crime ; dissent ; terrorism
china and kyrgyzstan pledge to make joint effort to crack down on terrorism and other threat to regional and global security .
china and kyrgyzstan agree in a joint communique that terrorism , separatism and extremism still pose major threat to regional security and stability .
the communique be sign by visit chinese premier wen jiabao and his kyrgyz counterpart nikolai tanayev on 040922 .
the communique say china and kyrgyzstan will strengthen coordination and cooperation among the relevant authority in accordance with the shanghai convention on combating terrorism , separatism and extremism and the china @-@ kyrgyzstan agreement on cooperation in combating terrorism , separatism and extremism .
the communique add that china and kyrgyzstan will continue to adopt strong measure within the framework of the shanghai cooperation organization ( sco ) in jointly fight all form of terrorism in order to maintain peace and tranquillity in china and kyrgyzstan and in the region as a whole .
china and kyrgyzstan agree that the crackdown on the terrorist force of eastern turkistan be a major part of the international anti @-@ terrorism campaign .
the so @-@ call eastern turkistan terrorist group comprise a number of secession @-@ mind terrorist cell .
the communique say that china and kyrgyzstan agree to promote consultation and cooperation on issue of common concern within the framework of the unite nation and other international organization .
china and kyrgyzstan say in the communique that peace , stability and a just and rational world political and economic order should be establish on the basis of the un charter and norm and principle of international law .
china and kyrgyzstan also agree that international dispute should be solve by peaceful mean and the unite nation should play a lead role in safeguard peace and security in the world and effort should be make to diversify mode of development .
china and kyrgyzstan further agree in the communique that the shanghai cooperation organization 's purpose and principle conform to reality and the development trend and the sco 's activity be conducive to regional peace and stability .
the communique say china and kyrgyzstan be willing to work together with other member of the shanghai cooperation organization and take effective measure in fight terrorism , separatism , extremism , drug traffic , illegal immigration and cross @-@ border crime .
the communique say china and kyrgyzstan be also ready to expand cooperation in economy and other field with other sco member , promote the relation between the sco and other country and international organization , and strengthen the sco 's role in maintain regional and global peace and development .
2004 @-@ 10 @-@ 09
viet nam ( vn ) ; germany ( de )
international ; government ; technology ; politics ; economy ; money ; leader
german chancellor gerhard schroeder attend meeting with vietnamese government leader after the 5 th asia @-@ europe meet summit in hanoi .
german and vietnamese official sign 5 document on financial , technical and business cooperation totaling over 260 million dollar .
media report state on 10 october 2004 that vietnamese and german official have pledge to further vietnamese and german relation in such field as investment , trade and technology and to support each other in the unite nation ( un ) .
german chancellor gerhard schroeder attend the 5 th asia @-@ europe meet summit in hanoi on 8 october 2004 and 9 october 2004 .
during separate talk and meeting with schroeder hold on 9 october 2004 vietnamese leader state that the vietnamese government support the german government 's bid for a permanent seat in the un security council and want to strengthen vietnamese relation with germany .
vietnamese prime minister phan van khai state that the visit by schroeder be important to the vietnam @-@ german relationship and the close cooperation between the 2 continent .
vietnamese and german official sign 5 document on financial , technical and business cooperation totaling over 260 million us dollar .
the document cover financial cooperation for 2 stage in the 2003 @-@ 2005 period and the purchase of 16 locomotive for the vietnam railway corporation and equipment for a local cement plant .
vietnamese state president tran duc luong state in a meet with schroeder that the vietnamese government would like to receive more technology transfer and experience from germany and that vietnam be develop under the industrialization process .
schroeder state that german official attach great importance to vietnam in an attempt to strengthen bilateral tie .
the german government support the vietnamese government 's bid for a non @-@ permanent membership of the un security council in the 2008 @-@ 2009 term and encourage small @- and medium @-@ size german enterprise to do business with vietnam .
the german government offer the vietnamese government official development assistance worth more than 480 million dollar in the 1990 @-@ 2003 period primarily for poverty reduction , agriculture development , healthcare and economic reform .
the vietnam @-@ germany trade volume rise 7.7 percent in 2003 to reach 1.4 billion dollar , of which 815.4 million dollar come from vietnamese export .
