xinhua news agency , seoul , august 31 st , by reporter shuifu tang
the first " le tian cup " china and korea go competition start today at fushan , the second largest city of korea .
in the first round of competition , the chinese team defeat the relatively stronger korean team with a score of 4 : 3 .
in the competition today , both side each have 7 go player participate .
weiping nie ( 9 th level ) , xiaoguang liu ( 9 th level ) , hao chang ( 6 th level ) and dayuan cao ( 9 th level ) from the chinese team defeat guibing cui ( 6 th level ) , xiuying zhang ( 9 th level ) , fengzhu xu ( 9 th level ) and xuange lin ( 8 th level ) from the korean team respectively .
among which , weiping nie , xiaoguang liu and hao chang both achieve victory in the middle game .
dayuan cao achieve victory with an advantage of seven and a half ' mu ' .
xunxuan cao ( 9 th level ) , changhao li ( 7 th level ) and changhe liu ( 6 th level ) from the korean team defeat jing liu ( 5 th level ) , xiaocun ma ( 9 th level ) and jianhong wang ( 7 th level ) from the chinese team respectively .
among which , xunxuan cao achieve a victory in the middle game .
changhao li and changhe liu achieve victory with advantage of six and a half ' mu ' and seven and a half ' mu ' respectively .
when receive reporter telephone interview , runan wang , leader of the chinese delegation present that , overall speak , the strength of the korean team be stronger than the chinese team .
however , the chinese team perform better today , and therefore achieve victory .
the performance of our young competitor , hao chang , be especially outstanding today , defeat fengzhu xu of the korean team in the middle game .
fengzhu xu have win many championship in international competition before .
he have achieve complete victory in nine game with chinese go player before .
the go team from china and korea will shift to seoul on september 1 st , and will hold the second competition in the le tian hotel on the 2 nd .
accord to the rule discuss and agree upon by both side , if the two team draw with 7 : 7 , then the final result will be determine by the result of the competition between weiping nie of the chinese team and xunxuan cao of the korean team .
the prize money of the competition this time be 100,000 us dollar , the team that win will get 70,000 us dollar , while the team that lose will get 30,000 us dollar .
( end )
xinhua news agency , rome , september 1 st , by reporter aiguo yang and changrui huang
the 1 - meter dive board preliminary of the seventh world swim championship be hold here this morning .
chinese competitor lan wei and sheng chen both receive qualification for the semi @-@ final .
in the preliminary , wei lan , who be 26 year old this year , from guangdong , with outstanding skill , occupy the lead position with a total score of 355.35 point .
sheng chen , who be 19 year old this year , from hubei , be temporarily in the sixth position , the a total score of 342.60 point .
the competitor who be temporarily in second place be the german athlete bao lizuo , with a total score of 355.02 point , slightly lower than wei lan .
the competitor from zimbabwe , si aiwan , who be temporarily in third place , have a total score of 354.39 point .
after the competition , the chief coach of the chinese dive team say to our agency 's reporter : " sheng chen be a little nervous today . "
he also say : " our athlete be not very use to carry out competition under strong sunlight . "
at home , they carry out indoor train mostly .
look like we still need to train more outdoors . "
he feel that , there be more new competitor from our country participate in this competition .
they still lack experience in international competition .
the preliminary competition for the women 's 10 - meter platform dive will be hold this afternoon .
mingxia fu , who win the championship for our country at the world championship and the olympic game , and the competitor from hebei , bin chi , who win the championship at the world cup will participate in the competition .
